These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, bird, goldfish
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, mexican, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway, van
1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is between the australian and the owner of the rat##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | rat    | bird      | hamster      | goldfish    |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | australian | mexican |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | subway     | bus     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, cucumber, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, egyptian, thai
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the egyptian is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the thai is on the far left##1
5. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
6. the dutch is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | peach     | corn       | cucumber    |
| Hobby         | photography | singing   | card-games | woodworking |
| Nationality   | thai    | egyptian | malaysian    | dutch        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, lily, orchid, iris
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cycling, sailing
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Flower      | rose | lily  | orchid    | iris |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Sport         | climbing    | sailing | baseball | cycling  |

