.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, lawyer, pilot, software-developer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, drama, scientific
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, august, april
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the pilot is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Job           | software-developer | lawyer        | engineer   | pilot  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy             | animation     | scientific | drama  |
| Birthday         | november           | april | december   | august |

