2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is basketball is the fan of trance##1
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person driving the bike##2
7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Sport          | baseball | basketball    | water-polo | weightlifting |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | trance    | punk      | blues     |
| Transport     | airplane | quad-bike | scooter   | bike      |

