.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, electronic, house, techno
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, ship, snowmobile, tram
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the fan of techno##1
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the snowmobile##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
7. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | juice   | lemonade    | coffee      | almond-milk |
| Music-Genre       | metal  | electronic | techno | house     |
| Transport   | scooter | ship        | snowmobile  | tram        |

