.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, fantasy, musical, spy
House: art-deco, modern, cottage, gothic-revival
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person watching spy movies and the cottage house##2
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is between the gothic-revival house and the person drinking water##2
6. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Beverage      | water      | sprite     | juice | coffee |
