5. the indian is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the argentine##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the malaysian##1
8. the person who growsiris is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking almond-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
