.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, blueberry, cranberry, plum
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dancer, journalist, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, sports, action, comedy
1. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the bartender##1
3. the person watching action movies is the person eating plum##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person watching sports movies is between the person eating avocado and the person eating cranberry##2
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
7. the person watching action movies is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | cranberry | blueberry  | avocado  | plum           |
| Job     | bartender | journalist | dancer   | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | sports       | epic | action  |

 